{"tid":2238062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"說好的巴鐵呢？習敗北未過數？巴基斯坦宣布禁TikTok 抵制不道德內容","createTime":"2020-10-10T20:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T20:12:43.000Z","uid":169310,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"080ef36a78e59bdad6b47873dd7ead5afee84af3","tid":2238062,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T20:05:52.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦電信部門週五（10月9日）宣布，禁止使用TikTok，原因是該社交媒體應用程序對「不道德和不雅」的內容不加過濾。<br />\n<br />\n這個消息證實了路透社此前的報導，巴基斯坦即將下令，禁用TikTok。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦電信管理局（PTA）在一份聲明中說：「鑑於來自社會不同階層對短片共享應用程序TikTok上不道德和不雅內容的投訴，PTA已發布指示，禁用該應用程序。」<br />\n<br />\n媒體無法立即與TikTok取得聯繫，就此事發表評論。<br />\n<br />\nPTA表示，TikTok已獲悉，該機構可對其決定進行審查，前提是TikTok採取了令人滿意的機制，對非法內容進行審核。<br />\n<br />\n三名高級政府官員在此前的報導中透露，將在幾個小時內正式宣布禁用TikTok。<br />\n<br />\n支那汁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.sina.cn/tech/2020-10-10/detail-iivhuipp8786414.d.html?fromtech=1&amp;from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2Ftech%2F2020-10-10%2Fdetail-iivhuipp8786414.d.html%3Ffromtech%3D1%26from%3Dwap&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=b124c69d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.cn/tech/2020-10-10/detail-iivhuipp8786414.d.html?fromtech=1&amp;from=wap</a>"},{"pid":"26552541bc449e9d8bbbf9473b474b15e0fbee3f","tid":2238062,"uid":169310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T20:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />說好的好兄弟，一帶一路去伊朗"},{"pid":"bfb1c6cef2daae1a70e0bbf157ca50e36003994b","tid":2238062,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T20:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出賣習大大，學埋美國d野"},{"pid":"204fbeb0f8c1914bac761ac709069920c922510d","tid":2238062,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T20:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7380900f18b9977b85694290878c1d2d27fb906f","tid":2238062,"uid":145307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T20:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}